isine is anchored by kimchi, a fermented vegetable dish, and features bold flavors from gochujang chili paste and soy sauce. BBQs with grilled beef bulgogi, bibimbap mixed rice bowls, and banchan side dishes define the cuisine.", "Thai cuisine is known for its bold balance of sweet, sour, salty, and spicy flavors in dishes like pad Thai, green curry, and tom yum soup. Fresh herbs, coconut milk, and fish sauce are staple ingredients.", "Mexican cuisine is a vibrant blend of indigenous Mesoamerican and Spanish influences, known for tacos, enchiladas, and mole sauces. It relies heavily on corn, beans, chili peppers, and fresh herbs like cilantro."], "scores": [0.9081983727165466, 0.8431257767956404, 0.8428674209386672, 0.8422380116156315, 0.8420036752311477], "model_name": "gte-small", "document_ids": ["Japanese", "Indian", "Korean", "Thai", "Mexican"]}}